# Plan: Upgrade Bun to 1.3.11

## Summary
Bump the Bun version from 1.3.9 to 1.3.11. There is a single version pin in the project.

## Changes

### 1. `package.json` (line 56)
Change `"packageManager": "bun@1.3.9"` → `"packageManager": "bun@1.3.11"`

This single change propagates to all CI workflows since they use `oven-sh/setup-bun@v2` without an explicit `bun-version`, auto-detecting from `packageManager`.

### 2. Regenerate lockfile
Run `bun install` to update `bun.lock` with the new version.

